@startuml
!include _style.puml
title TO-BE 01 · 로컬 우선 저장과 응답 유실 재시도

actor User
participant "App / Atlas iframe" as Editor
participant "Parent Coordinator" as Parent
participant "Normalized Adapter" as Adapter
participant "Persistence Kernel" as Kernel
database "IndexedDB" as IDB
participant "Outbox Worker" as Worker
participant "Writer Lock" as Lock
participant "Supabase RPC" as RPC
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "상태 UI" as UI

User -> Editor : 데이터 변경
Editor -> Editor : compatibility mirror\n+ dirty marker

alt Atlas 변경
  Editor -> Parent : snapshot(baseGeneration)
  Parent -> Parent : 현재 generation과 비교
  Parent --> Editor : ACK(generation+1)
  Parent -> Adapter : accepted Atlas + Bridge
else App 변경
  Editor -> Adapter : data-change
end

Adapter -> Adapter : App·Atlas·Bridge validate
Adapter -> Kernel : writeSnapshot(payload, remote)
Kernel -> IDB : snapshot + pending outbox\natomic transaction
IDB --> Kernel : read-back hash/count
Kernel -> Editor : compatibility mirror 갱신\n+ dirty marker 제거
Kernel -> UI : 로컬 · 저장됨\n서버 · 저장 대기

Worker -> Lock : workspace writer 획득
Worker -> IDB : claim oldest pending
IDB --> Worker : operationId · expectedRevision · payload
Worker -> RPC : ipe_commit_state(same operationId)
RPC -> DB : operation replay 확인\nrevision CAS\nappend + projection

alt 정상 응답
  DB --> RPC : revision N
  RPC --> Worker : revision N
else 서버 성공 후 응답 유실
  DB --> RPC : revision N committed
  RPC -x Worker : response lost
  Worker -> IDB : 같은 operationId를 pending으로 복귀
  Worker -> RPC : retry(same operationId)
  RPC -> DB : operationId replay lookup
  DB --> RPC : existing revision N
  RPC --> Worker : revision N · replayed
end

Worker -> RPC : ipe_load_head()
RPC -> DB : load head
DB --> RPC : revision N + payloadHash
RPC --> Worker : verified head
Worker -> IDB : operation acked\nfollowing pending expectedRevision=N
Worker -> UI : 서버 · rN 저장됨
Worker -> Lock : release

caption 로컬 완료는 IndexedDB 검증 시점이며, 서버 완료는 같은 operation의 head 검증 시점이다.
@enduml
